# Binary Search

```c
int binary_search(vector<int>v,int target) //find the position 
{
    int left=0;
    int right=v.size()-1;
    while(right=>left)
    {
        int mid=(right+left)/2;
        if(target==v[mid])  return left; //ÊúÄÂæåÁöÑËß£ left‰∏ãÁïå right‰∏äÁïå
        if(target>v[mid])   left=mid+1;
        else    // target<v[mid] 
